dr.who
======

This is a nonfunctional package acting as a name placeholder for a future open
source project.


Links
-----

TBD.


dr.who Installation
===================

This package does not need to be installed, as currently it exists solely to
reserve the package name.


Changelog
=========

What follows is a history of changes from release to release.


0.0.0 — Initial
---------------

This is the first release of ``dr.who`` that serves to reserve the package
name and nothing more.
